rawReviews.text: I recently had the pleasure of working with West Alabama Repair Services for some plumbing needs, and I couldn't be happier with the experience. They were quick to schedule and very communicative throughout the process, which made everything so much easier. They flushed our water heater and checked and fixed our sink efficiently. On top of their expertise, they have a wonderful personality and were incredibly kind, making the whole experience stress-free. Highly recommend them for any plumbing needs!

He is the only contractor i will ever use-it is rare to find someone whom you can tell them what u want and just let them go-no need to even touch base thru the process, he gets it handled-i even trust him to select colors/styles for me when im not available to do it. You def will not be disappointed with your experience with Lord’s Plumbing (Chet Smith).
